c:T550,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article","headline":"NVIDIA NemoClaw: Secure, Always-On AI Agents With One Command","description":"Announced at GTC 2026, NemoClaw is NVIDIA's open-source stack that adds privacy and security controls to OpenClaw. It bundles Nemotron models and the new OpenShell runtime into a single-command install for autonomous AI agents.","url":"https://github-checker-8.preview.emergentagent.com/ai-updates/nvidia-nemoclaw-secure-ai-agents","datePublished":"2026-03-16","dateModified":"2026-03-16","articleSection":"open-source","keywords":"NVIDIA, open-source, NemoClaw adds enterprise-grade privacy and security guardrails to OpenClaw — what Jensen called 'the operating system for personal AI.', Uses a privacy router that splits inference between local Nemotron models and cloud frontier models, keeping sensitive data on your hardware., Microsoft Security already reports a 160x improvement in finding AI-based attacks using Nemotron and OpenShell.","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Venkata Pagadala","url":"https://github-checker-8.preview.emergentagent.com"},"publisher":{"@type":"Person","name":"Venkata Pagadala","url":"https://github-checker-8.preview.emergentagent.com"},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://github-checker-8.preview.emergentagent.com/ai-updates/nvidia-nemoclaw-secure-ai-agents"}}2:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$c"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"AI Updates\",\"item\":\"https://github-checker-8.preview.emergentagent.com/ai-updates\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"NVIDIA NemoClaw: Secure, Always-On AI Agents With One Command\",\"item\":\"https://github-checker-8.preview.emergentagent.com/ai-updates/nvidia-nemoclaw-secure-ai-agents\"}]}"}}]